## Features

- `coally-sql`: run ad-hoc SQL over CSV/XLSX directly in Google Colab.

## Requirements

- Python 3.8+

## Installation

You can install _Coally_ via [pip] from [PyPI]:

```bash
pip install coally
```

## Quick start (Colab)

```python
from coally import AllySequelUI, UIOptions

# Full UI: drag & drop CSV/XLSX, run SQL, download result
AllySequelUI.show()
```

